0in%20his%20senior%20year%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%20He%20told%20Insider%20he%20picked%20his%20major%20because%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20and%20also%20because%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-salaries-what-you-make-google-apple-amazon-meta-ibm%5C%22%3Eindustry's%20salaries%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20back%20then%2C%20the%20salaries%20for%20computer%20science%20graduates%20already%20were%20among%20the%20highest%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20definitely%20contributed%20to%20me%20studying%20computer%20science.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20then%2C%20and%20this%20is%20now.%20The%20tech%20industry%20is%20in%20turmoil.%20Tech%20giants%20like%20Facebook%20and%20Google%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimpact-of-big-tech-layoffs-amazon-meta-microsoft-google-salesforce-2023-2%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20college%20students%20like%20Wong%2C%20job%20hunting%20has%20become%20a%20lot%20tougher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20tech%20companies%20in%20Singapore%20that%20used%20to%20hire%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20computer%20science%20majors%20from%20local%20universities%20are%20no%20longer%20hiring%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20said.%20Wong%20told%20Insider%20last%20month%20that%20he's%20applied%20to%2017%20jobs%20and%20has%20heard%20back%20from%20five%20companies.%20None%20of%20those%20responses%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20job%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20jobs%3A%20Internships%20are%20proving%20elusive%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D27be19d99cde9d72347dc9b1a9a6d9fd10a0363f1167aaf8ef173305d5570663%26postID%3D652f8cb1cb790ff8bec0249e%26postSlug%3Dcomputer-science-major-myth-job-security-money-salary-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%25