Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-hiring-spree-jobs-who-it-wants-and-amazon-salaries-2021-8%5C%22%3Ehiring%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fgoogle-parent-lay-off-12000-workers-memo-2023-01-20%2F%5C%22%3Esprees%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20recruiting%2C%20there%20is%20always%20this%20demand%20and%20supply%20question.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20demand%20was%20sky-high%20and%20there%20were%20just%20not%20enough%20people.%20So%20that%20drives%20up%20the%20salary%20and%20the%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Ang%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20were%20getting%20five%20offers%20on%20the%20table%20at%20one%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20the%20demand%20has%20died%20down.%20Companies%20are%20extremely%20cautious%20and%20what%20you%20have%20left%20behind%20is%20this%20surplus%20of%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Ang%20continued.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs%20now.%20It%20isn't%20like%20in%20the%20past%20when%20you%20received%20multiple%20invitations%20from%20companies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAng%20said%20these%20conditions%20have%20dampened%20the%20hiring%20demand%20for%20fresh%20graduates%20at%20tech%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20playing%20the%20short-term%20game%20right%20now.%20Everyone%20is%20trying%20to%20hold%20cash%2C%26quot%3B%20Ang%20said.%20%26quot%3BHiring%20fresh%20graduates%20isn't%20the%20best%20strategy%20because%20you%20need%20time%20to%20train%20them%20up.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comp.nus.edu.sg%2F~bleong%2F%5C%22%3EBen%20Leong%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20Insider%20it%20isn't%20so%20much%20a%20job%20shortage%20as%20it%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20students%20in%20Singapore%20who%20are%20qualified%20for%20computing%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%2