%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20ended%20when%20a%20rumor%20spread%20that%20the%20company%20was%20looking%20into%20installing%20listening%20devices%20in%20the%20trees%2C%20New%20York%20Times%20finance%20reporter%20Rob%20Copeland%20wrote%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fund%3A%20Ray%20Dalio%2C%20Bridgewater%20Associates%2C%20and%20the%20Unraveling%20of%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Legend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20did%20cameras%20cover%20seemingly%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20property%2C%20but%20they%20seemed%20to%20be%20watched%20in%20real%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20book%20alleged%2C%20adding%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-director-james-comey-time-at-bridgewater-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJames%20Comey%2C%20who%20would%20later%20become%20the%20head%20of%20the%20FBI%2C%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20Bridgewater's%20security%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20also%20said%20staff%20who%20left%20their%20desks%20would%20return%20to%20find%20sticky%20notes%20on%20their%20computer%20monitors%20telling%20them%20off%20for%20not%20putting%20up%20a%20screen%20saver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20tracked%20staffers'%20keystrokes%2C%20printouts%2C%20and%20photocopies%3B%20hid%20recording%20devices%20in%20light%20fittings%3B%20and%20required%20each%20email%20attachment%20staff%20sent%20to%20be%20individually%20approved%2C%20the%20book%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBridgewater%20called%20keystroke%20and%20printout%20surveillance%20claims%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20keystroke%20and%20printout%20was%20not%20tracked.%C2%A0What%20is%20true%20is%20that%20printouts%20had%20coversheets%20with%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person%20who%20printed%20them%2C%20as%20is%20typical%20in%20virtually%20all%20office%20settings%20with%20shared%20printers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaff%20at%20Bridgewater%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%2