021%2C%20Brooke%20and%20Chuck%20Anderson%20and%20their%20teenagers%20left%20a%20city%C2%A0to%20become%20homesteaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20built%20a%20cabin%20and%20added%20crops%20and%20animals%20to%20their%20285-acre%20property%20in%20rural%20Virginia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20thrilled%20they%20made%20the%20move%20even%20though%20parts%20of%20their%20new%20life%20take%20getting%20used%20to.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Brooke%20and%20Chuck%20Anderson%2C%2052%20and%2061%2C%20about%20their%20experience%20homesteading%20in%20Virginia's%20Blue%20Ridge%20Mountains%20with%20their%20two%20teenaged%20kids%20since%202021.%20The%20married%20couple%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40freedomranchhomestead7961%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Edocument%20their%20progress%20building%20their%20ranch%20on%20YouTube%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20have%20over%2039%2C000%20subscribers%2C%20plus%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffreedomranch_homestead%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20101%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20fourth-generation%20dairy%20farm%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20my%20intention%20was%20actually%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%20Ultimately%20I%20ended%20up%20moving%20to%20Raleigh%20in%20the%20'90s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20started%20dreaming%20of%20getting%20land%20for%20retirement%20purposes.%20Once%20the%20kids%20were%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%20we%20were%20going%20to%20move%20and%20start%20having%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20would%20go%20up%20to%20Wisconsin%20in%20the%20summers%2C%20I%20got%20a%20real%20taste%20of%20the%20lifestyle.%20It%20was%20something%20that%20brought%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20pleasure%20and%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20got%20on%20board%20with%20doing%20this.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20and%20purchase%20the%20property%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20something%20that%20was%20going%20to%20be%20very%20beneficial%20for%20us%2C%20even%20though%20I'd%20never%20done%20it%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20wanted%20a%20forest%20and%20pasture%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20within%2030%20minutes%20of%20a%20more%20developed%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20we'd%20already%20purchased%20the%20land%20with%20a%20long-term%20plan%20to%20move%20up%20here%2C%20COVID%20fast-tracked%20that.%20It%20got%20people%20thinking%20about%20wanting%20to%20be%20outside%20and%20not%20be%20cooped%20up%20in%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20passed%20away%20from%20COVID.%20It%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20we%20waiting%20for%3F%26quot%3B%20Life%20is%20short.%20We%20already%20had%20the%20dream.%20We%20knew%20what%20we%20were%20going%20to%20do%2C%20and%20those%20kinds%20of%20life%20events%20just%20change%20your%20timeline%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20on%20our%20way%20to%20fully%20living%20off%20of%20the%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We're%20in%20southwestern%20Virginia%20in%20the%20Blue%20Ridge%20Mountains%2C%20just%20south%20of%20Blacksburg%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Virginia%20Tech%20area.%20The%20property%20is%20exactly%20three%20hours%20from%20Raleigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20285%20acres.%20It%20was%20about%20%244%2C000%20an%20acre%20%E2%80%94%20in%202020%2C%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20affordable%20than%20it%20is%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Today%2C%20this%20property%20would%20probably%20go%20for%20more%20like%20%248%2C000%20an%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20we%20bought%20it%2C%20there%20was%20nothing.%20There%20was%20absolutely%20nothing.%20We%20didn't%20even%20have%20an%20address%20for%20a%20mailbox.%20There%20was%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20my%20father%20died%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20for%20some%20white%20pine%20lumber%20from%20our%20farm%20in%20Wisconsin%20that%20he%20and%20I%20cut%20in%20the%20'80s.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20we%20take%20some%20of%20that%20lumber%20down%20to%20Virginia%20and%20use%20it%20to%20build%20a%20shed%20in%20your%20honor%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20that's%20our%20first%20building.%20So%20that's%20what%20we%20did.%20We%20named%20it%20Grumpy's%20Garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shed%20with%20a%20sign%20that%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BGrumpy's%20Garage.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a5ec83cc84b4dfafdbed0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrumpy's%20Garage.%3Cp%3EBrooke%20Anderson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20camped%20in%20it%20a%20lot%20while%20we%20were%20building%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20infrastructure.%20We%20built%20an%20outhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20moved%20here%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20August%20of%202021%20to%20get%20the%20kids%20in%20school.%20They%20started%20a%20couple%20days%20after%20we%20moved%20here%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20have%20a%20place%20to%20live%20besides%20Grumpy's%20Garage.%20So%20we%20rented%20an%20Airbnb%20for%20a%20month.%20Then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_onHPXHcygc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewe%20started%20building%20a%20yurt%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lived%20in%20the%20yurt%20with%20no%20electricity%20or%20running%20water%20or%20plumbing.%20We%20thought%20it%20would%20only%20be%20a%20four-%20or%20five-month%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20ended%20up%20being%20in%20it%20for%20two%20years%20as%20we%20got%20the%20log%20home%20ready%20to%20be%20occupied.%20We%20went%20through%20two%20winters%20in%20the%20yurt%2C%20heating%20with%20wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20getting%20a%20well%20put%20in%2C%20getting%20electrical%20put%20in%2C%20getting%20the%20mail%20to%20recognize%20us.%20It%20was%20so%20stressful%20getting%20an%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20got%20a%20horse%20shed%2C%20hog%20pen%2C%20yurt%2C%20outhouse%2C%20and%20the%20log%20cabin.%20We%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20left%20to%20do%2C%20but%20the%20cabin%20is%20livable%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crane%20lifting%20a%20piece%20of%20lumber%20into%20a%20log%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a5f4636d588dc55cc29b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Andersons'%20cabin%20being%20built.%3Cp%3EBrooke%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20we%20built%20a%20huge%20kiln%20to%20dry%20logs%20in%20when%20we%20harvest%20them.%20That%20did%20not%20work.%20We%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20chicken%20coop%20and%20a%20storage%20facility.%20It%20was%20an%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eepic%20fail%20by%20our%20own%20design.%20But%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20phenomenal%20chicken%20coop%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20way%20taller%20than%20most%20chicken%20coops%20need%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20us%2C%20homesteading%20is%20being%20in%20a%20position%20where%20we%20can%20survive%20independently%20without%20outside%20resources%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20have%20electricity%20and%20all%20the%20creature%20comforts%20of%20home.%20I%20still%20go%20to%20the%20store%20to%20get%20stuff%2C%20but%20we're%20in%20a%20position%20where%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20all%20that%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20have%20animals%2C%20crops%2C%20and%20a%20log%20cabin%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Our%20beef%20cattle%20are%20going%20to%20be%20delivering%20calves%20in%20a%20few%20months.%20We've%20had%20baby%20chicks%2C%20we've%20had%20piglets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20piglets%20in%20a%20pen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a5e9a36d588dc55cc28fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20piglets%20on%20the%20Andersons'%20homestead.%3Cp%3EBrooke%20Anderson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20had%20100%20chickens.%20We're%20down%20to%2035.%20There%20are%20animals%20that%20keep%20eating%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20is%20a%20wild%20kingdom.%20We've%20got%20bears%2C%20raccoons%2C%20coyotes%2C%20foxes%2C%20hawks%20%E2%80%94%20eating%20chicken.%20We're%20building%20stronger%20enclosures.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20be%20able%20to%20free%20range%2C%20but%20nature%20is%20pretty%20wild%20out%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20got%20a%20very%20large%20garden.%20We've%20had%20gardens%20that%20produce%20fruits%2C%20watermelons%2C%20cucumbers%2C%20zucchini%2C%20corn%2C%20potatoes%2C%20and%20tomatoes.%20We%20have%20apple%20trees%20that%20we%20planted%2C%20peach%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20focused%20intensely%20on%20it%20just%20because%20of%20prioritization%20of%20all%20the%20other%20activities%2C%20like%20getting%20shelter%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20weeds%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20failures%20along%20the%20way.%20So%20that's%20part%20of%20our%20journey.%20One%20of%20the%20things%20that%20Brooke%20does%20is%20to%20document%20not%20just%20the%20fun%2C%20good%20success%20stories%2C%20but%20also%20the%20things%20didn't%20go%20so%20well.%20It%20doesn't%20work%20out%20all%20the%20time%20very%20perfectly%2C%20but%20we're%20trying%20our%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAll%20of%20the%20kids%2C%20they've%20learned%20how%20to%20run%20a%20drill%2C%20how%20to%20run%20a%20chop%20saw%2C%20how%20to%20drive%20a%20tractor%2C%20birth%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epiglets.%20We've%20done%20it%20together%20as%20a%20family%20and%20grown%20closer%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20only%20thing%20we're%20missing%20right%20now%20is%20the%20dairy%20cow%20%E2%80%94%20and%20solar%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomesteading%20lacks%20the%20convenience%20(and%20cleanliness)%20of%20city%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20used%20to%20live%20a%20half-mile%20from%20a%20grocery%20store%20in%20Raleigh.%20Being%20able%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20forgot%20this%20for%20dinner%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20run%20to%20the%20store%20real%20quick%26quot%3B%3F%20You%20can't%20do%20that%20here%20%E2%80%94%20the%20store's%20a%20half-hour%20away.%20That%2C%20for%20me%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20downfall%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that's%20been%20challenging%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20because%20we%20have%20a%20daughter%20who's%20very%20social%20and%20doesn't%20drive%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20the%20car%20for%20an%20hour%20almost%20every%20day.%20She%20goes%20to%20high%20school%20about%20a%20half%20hour%20away%20from%20here.%20Then%20if%20she%20wants%20to%20go%20to%20the%20mall%2C%20that's%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20away%20in%20Roanoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe's%20riding%20horses%20and%20she's%20learning%20how%20to%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCutting_(sport)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting%20of%20cows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20rodeo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you've%20ever%20watch%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe's%20doing%20really%20well%20at%20it.%20And%20most%20recently%20she%20took%20up%20bow%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20have%20dirt%20roads%2C%20and%20having%20dirty%20cars%20all%20the%20time%20is%20kind%20of%20annoying.%20A%20lot%20of%20dirt%20everywhere%2C%20but%20you%20get%20used%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20peace%20and%20freedom%20of%20our%20new%20life%20are%20unmatched%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooke%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We're%20not%20very%20young.%20What%20we're%20doing%20is%20very%20physical%20%E2%80%94%20just%20feeding%20the%20animals%20and%20lifting%20up%20the%20heavy%20bags%20of%20food%20and%20carrying%20the%20big%20five-gallon%20buckets%20of%20water%2C%20and%20building%20things.%20It%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20physical%20work%20than%20I%20had%20thought%20that%20it%20would%20ever%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20motivates%20me%20to%20stay%20in%20shape%20because%20if%20we%20plan%20on%20doing%20this%20for%20the%20next%2010%2C%2020%20years%2C%20we%20can't%20lose%20any%20muscle%20mass.%20We%20got%20to%20stay%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChuck%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20have%20nine%20miles%20of%20trails%20that%20we've%20already%20mapped%20out%20on%20our%20property%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20absolute%20stunning%20beauty.%20It's%20almost%20like%20having%20our%20own%20park.%20We%20can%20hike%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20and%20not%20run%20into%20another%20single%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20place%20becomes%20part%20of%20our%20DNA.%20We%20just%20want%20to%20be%20here%2C%20and%20it's%20so%20peaceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomesteading-family-property-life-challenges-lessons-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699388851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a5fd7b788914e55519dae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomesteading-family-property-life-challenges-lessons-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brooke%20and%20Chuck%20Anderson%20left%20a%20city%20to%20homestead%20on%20285%20acres.%20Their%20chickens%20keep%20getting%20eaten%2C%20but%20they've%20found%20peace%20like%20never%20before.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomesteading-family-property-life-challenges-lessons-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seals%20with%20funny%20hats%20discovered%20a%20hidden%20canyon%20over%20a%20mile%20deep%20under%20Antarctica%20and%20scientists%20want%20to%20honor%20the%20animals%20by%20naming%20it%20after%20them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20seal%20with%20a%20tracker%20adhered%20to%20its%20fur%20sitting%20in%20some%20grass%20with%20a%20rainbow%20behind%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a4eb436d588dc55cc1685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222420%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Insider%2C%20scientist%20Clive%20McMahon%20called%20the%20seals%20they%20adhered%20trackers%20to%20heroes.%3Cp%3ERobert%20Harcourt%2C%20IMOS%20Animal%20Tagging%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EScientists%20put%20trackers%20on%20Antarctic%20seals%20to%20help%20them%20map%20the%20ocean%20floor.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20deep-diving%20seals%20revealed%20a%20massive%20underwater%20canyon%20over%20a%20mile%20deep.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20canyon%20may%20help%20scientists%20predict%20how%20the%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheet%20will%20react