bc11ee82d1411d0a82b82a%2523Sec13%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejournal%20Nature%20Communications%20Earth%20%26amp%3B%20Environment.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20seal%20scientists%20aren't%20just%20helping%20us%20map%20unknown%20parts%20of%20the%20ocean%2C%20they're%20also%20helping%20scientists%20predict%20how%20the%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheet%20might%20react%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20per%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20this%20canyon%20can%20show%20us%20about%20the%20future%20of%20Antarctica's%20ice%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224976%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20marine%20research%20expedition%20in%20Antarctica.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a4f14b788914e555189c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPerforming%20marine%20research%20in%20Antarctica%20can%20be%20complicated%20by%20intense%20weather.%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Marlow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20ocean%20geography%20helps%20scientists%20predict%20how%20Antarctica's%20ice%20sheet%C2%A0has%20reacted%20to%20global%20climate%20change%20in%20the%20past.%20Like%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrand-canyon-history-100-year-anniversary-2019-2%5C%22%3EGrand%20Canyon%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shows%20the%20pathway%20of%20an%20ancient%20river%2C%20these%20underwater%20features%20also%20give%20us%20an%20idea%20about%20how%20water%20moved%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20mapping%20these%20deep%20troughs%20and%20mountain%20ranges%20we%20have%20therefore%20added%20a%20key%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20to%20help%20understand%20how%20the%20East%20Antarctic%20Ice%20Sheet%20may%20have%20responded%20to%20past%20change%20and%20how%20it%20may%20do%20so%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Fausto%20Ferraccioli%2C%20who%20studies%20these%20underwater%20formations%20and%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fmach%2Fscience%2Fvast-hidden-canyons-mountain-ranges-discovered-antarctica-ncna877621%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20NBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20give%20scientists%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20thinner%20points%20of%20the%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheets%2C%20cluing%20them%20into%20what%20is%20more%20at%20risk%20of%20melting.%20Water%20from%20the%20canyon%20can%20move%20around%20the%20ice%20sheet%2C%20which%20may%20melt%20it%20more%20quickly%20when%20it's%20warmed%20by%20climate%20change%2C%20the%20researchers%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fantarctic.org.au%2Fseals-uncover-new-ocean-depths-in-east-antarctica%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAustralian%20Center%20for%20Excellence%20in%20Aquatic%20Science%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20contributed%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20knowledge%20is%20essential%20for%20scientists%20trying%20to%20measure%20icesheet%20melt%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20Clive%20McMahon%2C%20the%20lead%20researcher%20on%20the%20paper%2C%20told%20the%20ACEAS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20they%20got%20the%20hat%20on%20the%20seal%C2%A0%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20seal%20sticking%20its%20head%20out%20of%20water%20with%20the%20tracker%20on%20its%20head.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a4eb4b788914e55518982%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20trackers%20were%20adhered%20to%20the%20fur%20on%20the%20seals%20head%2C%20which%20the%20researchers%20said%20sheds%20annually.%3Cp%3EClive%20McMahon%2C%20IMOS%20Animal%20Tagging%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20extreme%20temperatures%20and%20pressure%20deep%20underwater%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20build%20and%20operate%20ships%20that%20can%20dive%20into%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20oceans%20and%20return%20intact.%20That's%20where%20deep-diving%20seals%20come%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntarctic%20seals%2C%20like%20the%2050%20Weddell%20seals%20and%20215%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felephant-seals-sleep-spiral-deep-ocean-order-avoid-predators-2023-4%5C%22%3Esouthern%20elephant%20seals%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20tagged%2C%20regularly%20travel%20to%20great%20depths%20of%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffmars.2021.751840%2Ffull%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearchers%20from%20the%20seal%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20placing%20sensors%20on%20the%20animals%2C%20which%20were%20headed%20down%20into%20the%20water%20anyway%2C%20could%20be%20a%20cheaper%20and%20more%20effective%20way%20to%20map%20the%20features%20of%20the%20Antarctic%20Ocean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20this%20by%20attaching%20the%20sensors%20%26quot%3Bwith%20adhesive%20to%20the%20hair%20on%20the%20seals'%20heads.%26quot%3B%20Seals%20shed%20this%20hair%20each%20year%2C%20which%C2%A0means%20the%20seals%20performed%20their%20duty%20without%20any%20pain%2C%20the%20Australian%20Antarctic%20Program%20Partnership%2C%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAnt_Partnership%2Fstatus%2F1689140900189110272%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20on%C2%A0X%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20response%20to%20concerns%20about%20the%20animal's%20wellbeing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseals-with-trackers-discover-hidden-antarctic-canyon-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699388572000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a4ec3b788914e5551898d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseals-with-trackers-discover-hidden