-67350709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67350709.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67350709.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hunter%20Biden%20special%20counsel%20denies%20political%20meddling%20in%20testimony%20to%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699384125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F6152%2Fproduction%2F_131641942_f2892ae28dbba8efc16cdeb8e74536a90bcf6400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67348412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Special%20Counsel%20David%20Weiss%20says%20at%20no%20time%20has%20his%20probe%20been%20blocked%20by%20the%20justice%20department.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67348412%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67348412.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67348412.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20Half%20As%20Bad%20As%20Delhi%2C%20But%20Mumbai%20Gets%20Special%20Respiratory%20ICU%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas%20hogging%20the%20limelight%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20Mumbai%20has%20been%20flying%20under%20the%20radar%20nationally.%20But%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%20is%20so%20bad%20that%20not%20only%20was%20it%20among%20the%20world's%20most%20polluted%20cities%20on%20Sunday%2C%20but%20a%20hospital%20had%20to%20also%20set%20up%20a%20special%20Intensive%20Respiratory%20Care%20Unit%20to%20attend%20to%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20despite%20the%20city's%20geographical%20advantage%20of%20being%20located%20on%20the%20coast%20and%20being%20surrounded%20by%20water%20on%20three%20sides%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20strong%20winds%20blowing%20away%20most%20of%20the%20pollutants%20in%20the%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENDTV%20visited%20the%20special%20respiratory%20ICU%20started%20by%20Global%20Hospitals%20in%20Central%20Mumbai's%20Parel%20and%20found%20that%20cases%20of%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20problems%20have%20doubled%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20went%20to%20a%20construction%20site%20at%20one%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government's%20flagship%20projects%2C%20the%20coastal%20road%2C%20and%20found%20the%20civic%20body%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20violating%20its%20own%20guidelines%20aimed%20at%20combating%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20ICU%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Prashant%20Borade%2C%20Director%2C%20Department%20of%20Critical%20Care%2C%20Global%20Hospitals%20said%20that%2C%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20they%20have%20been%20seeing%20patients%20who%20are%20reporting%20breathlessness%20even%20after%20getting%20cured%20of%20a%20lung%20infection.%20These%20patients%20are%20then%20diagnosed%20with%20inflammation%20in%20their%20lungs%20or%20hyperacute%20airway%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENearly%2050%25%2C%20or%20one%20in%20two%2C%20of%20all%20patients%20with%20such%20symptoms%20who%20are%20visiting%20the%20Outpatient%20Department%20are%20having%20to%20be%20admitted%20for%20at%20least%20one%20or%20two%20days.%20Almost%2030%25%20are%20needing%20admission%20to%20the%20ICU%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20cases%20of%20lung%20cancer%20are%20also%20rising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20cases%20have%20gone%20up%20since%20Covid%20hit%20and%20Dr%20Borade%20attributed%20the%20rise%20partly%20to%20viruses%20becoming%20more%20virulent%20and%20causing%20long-term%20problems%20in%20the%20lungs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20that%2C%20the%20other%20cause%20is%20air%20pollution.%20The%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20is%20increasing%20every%20day%20and%20so%20is%20particulate%20matter%20of%20less%20than%2010%20microns.%20These%20particles%20enter%20the%20lungs.%20If%20they%20are%20over%2010%20microns%2C%20they%20may%20get%20filtered%20at%20the%20nose%20level%20or%20airway%20level%2C%20but%20those%20under%2010%20microns%20don't%2C%20and%20cause%20these%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdt2ge5i8_mumbai-special-respiratory-icu_625x300_07_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20said%20the%20hospital%20has%20seen%20a%20100%25%20increase%20in%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20illnesses.%20Patients%20with%20chronic%20respiratory%20illnesses%20are%20getting%20worse%20and%20even%20those%20without%20them%20are%20going%20to%20the%20hospital%20with%20hyperacute%20airway%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20symptoms%20of%20such%20airway%20diseases%20are%20breathlessness%2C%20wheezing%20and%20chronic%20cough%2C%20which%20doesn't%20go%20away%20even%20when%20they%20are%20given%20antibiotics.%20It%20looks%20like%20asthma%20but%20it%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20asthma...%20We%20have%20to%20give%20inhalers%20and%20some%20patients%20even%20need%20steroids.%20Pollution%20reduces%20the%20immunity%20of%20the%20lungs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20In%20an%20alarming%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Borade%20said%20he%20is%20seeing%20such%20symptoms%20in%20young%20patients%20too%2C%20and%20many%20of%20them%20have%20to%20be%20admitted%20to%20the%20ICU.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20polluted%20air%20may%20be%20leading%20to%20heart%20diseases%20and%20heart%20attacks%20over%20the%20long%20term.%20Lung%20cancer%20cases%20have%20also%20gone%20up%20slightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInhaling%20this%20polluted%20air%20is%20like%20smoking%201%2C000%20cigarettes%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20get%20worse%20after%20Diwali.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20government%20taking%20several%20measures%20to%20curb%20the%20bursting%20of%20firecrackers.%20Air%20pollution%20also%20goes%20up%20during%20the%20winter%20and%20that%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20we%20have%20opened%20this%20special%20ICU%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Borade%20also%20said%20that%20a%20tuberculosis%20patient%20who%20had%20been%20discharged%20and%20had%20been%20improving%20has%20had%20to%20get%20treatment%20again%2C%20and%20said%20the%20pollution%20may%20be%20a%20cause%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Can%20You%20Do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20said%20it%20is%20imperative%20for%20patients%20with%20chronic%20lung%20conditions%20like%20bronchitis%2C%20asthma%20or%20lung%20damage%20to%20wear%20masks%20when%20they%20are%20stepping%20out.%20This%20is%20also%20true%2C%20he%20said%2C%20for%20the%20immunosuppressed%2C%20like%20the%20elderly%20and%20those%20with%20diabetes%20and%20cancer.%20He%20also%20advised%20against%20evening%20walks%20and%20said%20people%20should%20opt%20for%20an%20early%20morning%20walk%20in%20places%20with%20greenery%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstruction%20Violations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENDTV%20also%20visited%20a%20construction%20site%20of%20the%20flagship%2029.5-km%20coastal%20road%20project%20-%20which%20will%20stretch%20from%20Marine%20Lines%20in%20the%20south%20to%20Kandivali%20in%20the%20north%20-%20and%20found%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20flouting%20its%20own%20pollution%20guidelines.%20The%20civic%20body%20had%2C%20incidentally%2C%20issued%20over%20400%20notices%20for%20violating%20these%20guidelines%20in%20a%20single%20day%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%