%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney%20(P%26amp%3BW)%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20carrier%2C%20which%20had%20a%20fleet%20of%20334%20planes%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20will%20face%20capacity%20issues%20due%20to%20the%20significant%20number%20of%20grounded%20aircraft%20in%20the%20March%20quarter%20even%20as%20various%20measures%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20address%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20recently%20received%20additional%20information%20on%20the%20powder%20metal%20issue%20from%20Pratt%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney%20and%20based%20on%20our%20preliminary%20assessment%20of%20this%2C%20we%20anticipate%20Aircraft%20on%20Ground%20(AOG)%20in%20the%20range%20of%20mid-thirties%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20(Jan-Mar2024)%20due%20to%20accelerated%20engine%20removals.%20These%20groundings%20will%20be%20incremental%20to%20the%20current%20AOGs%2C%26quot%3B%20IndiGo%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20P%26amp%3BW%20highlighted%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20powder%20metal%20issue%20that%20has%20affected%20its%20new%20generation%20GTF%20aircraft%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlobally%2C%20we%20understand%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20incremental%20engines%20ranging%20between%20600-700%20are%20being%20removed%20for%20accelerated%20inspections%20and%20shop%20visits%20between%202023%20and%202026%20and%20two-thirds%20of%20these%20engine%20removals%20are%20planned%20for%202023%20and%20early%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20IndiGo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20the%20airline%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20P%26amp%3BW%20on%20more%20information%20and%20addressing%20the%20situation%20and%20implementing%20mitigation%20measures%20to%20minimise%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20AOGs%20on%20its%20capacity%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20confirm%20our%20earlier%20capacity%20guidance%20for%20the%20entire%20FY23-