ing%2C%20Mrs%20Webster's%20husband%20found%20her%20unconscious%20with%20a%20brown%20liquid%20coming%20out%20of%20her%20mouth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20had%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20brown%20stuff%20coming%20out%20of%20her%20mouth%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20she%20wasn't%20breathing%20and%20started%20doing%20CPR%2C%26quot%3B%20Roy%20Webster%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F9now.nine.com.au%2F60-minutes%2Fozempic-weight-loss-drug-side-effects%2Ff439790a-0587-449f-b99c-121be6dcd5aa%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E60%20Minutes%20Australia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20pouring%20out%2C%20and%20I%20turned%20her%20onto%20the%20side%20because%20she%20couldn't%20breathe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMrs%20Webster%20died%20that%20night%20and%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20death%20was%20listed%20as%20acute%20gastrointestinal%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20knew%20that%20could%20happen%2C%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20taking%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20grieving%20husband%20told%20the%20media%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20thought%20you%20could%20die%20from%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20doctors%20have%20not%20linked%20Mrs%20Webster's%20death%20to%20her%20Ozempic%20and%20Saxenda%20usage%2C%20her%20husband%20believes%20the%20drugs%20were%20the%20culprits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20shouldn't%20be%20gone%2C%20you%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Roy%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20not%20worth%20it%2C%20it's%20not%20worth%20it%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20Ozempic%2C%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20said%20the%20recurring%20stomach%20complication%20ileus%20was%20only%20reported%20after%20what%20it%20calls%20its%20%26quot%3Bpost-marketing%20setting%26quot%3B%2C%20suggesting%20they%20only%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20problem%20after%20the%20drug%20was%20released%20and%20became%20a%20pharmaceutical%20blockbuster.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publi