22%3E%E2%80%8BMany%20Bollywood%20actors%20have%20ventured%20into%20the%20world%20of%20reality%20television%20by%20participating%20as%20contestants%20in%20various%20shows.%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%20Shows%20Every%20Third%20Family%20Poor%3A%20Nitish%20Announces%20Rs%202%20Lakh%20Aid%2C%20Wants%2075%25%20Reservation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07214142%2FF-AjAdfbYAA6UOc.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20another%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20to%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%2C%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%207%2C%20announced%20a%20slew%20of%20welfare%20benefits%20for%20poor%20families%20in%20the%20state%20immediately%20after%20releasing%20the%20socio-economic%20data%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%20The%20socio-economic%20data%20was%20eagerly%20awaited%20after%20the%20Bihar%20govt%20released%20its%20caste%20survey%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20showed%20that%20about%2094%20lakh%20families%20%E2%80%93%2034.13%25%20of%20the%20total%202.76%20crore%20families%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20are%20economically%20poor%20and%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Nitish%20called%20for%2065%25%20of%20government%20jobs%20and%20education%20to%20be%20reserved%20for%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%20and%20STs.%20Scheduled%20Castes%20should%20have%2020%25%20reservation%2C%20while%20OBCs%20and%20EBCs%20together%20should%20get%2043%25%20reservation%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20remaining%202%25%20should%20be%20reserved%20for%20STs%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%20With%20the%2010%25%20reservation%20for%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20(EWS)%20among%20the%20upper%20castes%2C%20a%20fourth%20of%20government%20jobs%20and%20seats%20in%20educational%20institutes%20will%20be%20reserved%20if%20the%20move%20is%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20Rs%202%20lakh%20will%20be%20provided%20as%20a%20one-time%20financial%20assistance%20to%20the%2094%20lakh%20families%20who%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20month.%20The%20state%20government%20will%20spend%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20crore%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20for%20the%20economically%20poor%2C%20he%20said.%20Of%20these%20families%2C%20those%20who%20are%20homeless%20will%20be%20provided%20an%20additional%20Rs%2040%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighest%20poverty%20among%20SCs%2C%20STs%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20highest%20proportion%20of%20poor%20families%20was%20among%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20the%20data%20showed.%20Among%20families%20from%20SC%20communities%2C%20which%20constitute%2019.65%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20in%20the%20state%2C%2042.93%25%20are%20poor.%20Among%20the%20minuscule%20ST%20population%2C%20just%201.68%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%2042.7%25%20are%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%2033.16%25%20of%20families%20classified%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20are%20poor%20and%2033.58%25%20of%20families%20classified%20as%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs)%20are%20poor%2C%20revealed%20the%20data.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%5C%22%3Ecaste%20data%20of%20the%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20while%20OBCs%20constitute%2027.13%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20EBCs%20comprise%2036.01%25.%20Among%20upper%20caste%20families%2C%20who%20constitute%2015%2C52%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%2025.09%25%20are%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20OBCs%2C%20the%20dominant%20Yadav%20caste%20has%20reported%20the%20highest%20poor%20population.%20A%20third%20of%20Yadavs%2C%20who%20constitute%2014.26%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20are%20poor%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20Of%20the%20Kushwaha%20(Koiri)%20caste%2C%2034.32%25%20of%20the%20families%20are%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20SCs%2C%20Musahars%20have%20the%20worst%20socio-economic%20conditions.%20About%2054.56%25%20of%20the%208%2C73%2C281%20families%20of%20Musahars%20are%20poor.%20Of%20the%20Bhuiyan%20community%2C%2053.55%25%20of%20families%20are%20poor.%20Similarly%2C%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20families%20from%20Dom%20and%20Bhogta%20communities%20are%20living%20in%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20upper%20castes%2C%20Bhumihars%20have%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20poor%20families.%20While%20the%20caste%20census%20data%20showed%20that%20Bhumihars%20constitute%202.86%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%2027.58%25%20of%20them%20are%20poor.%20A%20quarter%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20population%20in%20Bihar%20(3.65%25%20of%20the%20total%20population)%20is%20poor%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20A%20quarter%20of%20Rajputs%20are%20also%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslim%20communities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20Muslims%2C%20the%20Shershahbadi%20and%20Dhuniya%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20classified%20as%20EBCs%20%E2%80%93%20have%2031.99%25%20and%2031.42%25%20families%20living%20in%20poverty.%20About%2026.77%25%20of%20families%20of%20the%20Momin%20caste%20and%2029.67%25%20of%20families%20of%20Rain%20or%20Kunjra%20are%20also%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20backward%20classes%2C%20the%20Surjapuri%20Muslims%20have%20the%20highest%20percentage%20of%20poor%20families%20(29.33).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20upper-caste%20Muslims%2C%20about%2025.84%25%20of%20Sheikh%20families%20are%20poor.%20Whereas%20in%20the%20Pathan%20caste%2C%20about%2022.20%25%20of%20the%20families%20are%20poor%20and%2017.61%25%20of%20Syed%20families%20live%20in%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fhow-true-is-the-claim-that-bihar-caste-survey-is-promoting-casteism%5C%22%3EHow%20True%20Is%20the%20Claim%20That%20Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%20Is%20%E2%80%98Promoting%20Casteism%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpper%20castes%20well%20educated%2C%20represented%20in%20government%20jobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar%20has%20a%20total%20of%2013.07%20crore%20population%2C%20out%20of%20which%2020.47%20lakh%20persons%20are%20in%20government%20jobs.%20Of%20these%2020.49%20lakh%20people%2C%206.41%20lakh%20persons%20are%20from%20upper%20castes%2C%206.21%20lakh%20persons%20are%20from%20OBC%20communities%2C%204.61%20lakh%20persons%20are%20from%20EBC%20communities%2C%202.91%20lakh%20persons%20are%20from%20SC%20communities%20and%2030%2C164%20persons%20are%20from%20ST%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20upper%20castes%20constitute%2015%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20they%20are%20overrepresented%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20the%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20education%20front%20too%2C%20backward%20communities%20are%20lagging.%20Among%20upper%20castes%2C%2013.41%25%20are%20graduates.%20Among%20BCs%2C%20just%206.77%25%20are%20while%20just%204.27%25%20of%20EBCs%20are.%20Among%20SCs%2C%20only%203.05%25%20of%20the%20population%20are%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar%20is%20among%20the%20states%20which%20have%20high%20out-migration%20for%20low-paying%20jobs.%20The%20latest%20data%20revealed%20that%20about%2046%20lakh%20people%20of%20Bihar%20are%20living%20in%20other%20states%20to%20make%20their%20livelihood%2C%20whereas%205.52%20lakh%20people%20are%20living%20outside%20to%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EData%20revealed%20that%20only%2011.44%25%20population%20of%20upper%20castes%20are%20labourers%20and%20masons%2C%20whereas%2013.74%25%20of%20BCs%2C%2018.62%25%20of%20EBCs%2C%2021.38%25%20of%20SCs%20and%2018.51%25%20of%20STs%20are%20working%20as%20labourers%20and%20masons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENitish%20wants%20to%20hike%20reservation%20to%2065%25%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20socio-economic%20data%20was%20released%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20proposed%20to%20increase%20caste-based%20reservations%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%20Currently%2C%20there%20is%20a%20Supreme%20Court-imposed%20ceiling%20of%2050%25%20reservations%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs.%20Chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20proposed%20to%20increase%20the%20reservation%20to%2065%25%20%E2%80%93%20excluding%20the%2010%25%20for%20EWS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20proposal%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20will%20have%2020%25%20reservation%20and%20OBCs%20and%20EBCs%20together%20will%20get%2043%25%20reservation.%20STs%20will%20get%202%25%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20since%20OBCs%20should%20also%20get%20reservations%20according%20to%20their%20population%2C%20the%2050%25%20ceiling%20should%20be%20abolished%20and%20the%20quota%20should%20be%20increased%20to%2065%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMandal%20parties%20have%20long%20been%20arguing%20that%20a%20proper%20caste%20census%20could%20help%20the%20government%20channel%20welfare%20benefits%20in%20a%20scientific%20way.%20The%20Congress%20too%20has%20joined%20the%20bandwagon%20now%20and%20has%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3Enationwide%20caste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20state-level%20caste%20surveys%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Bihar%20if%20elected%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Claims%20of%20development%20debunked%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEconomists%20say%20that%20the%20poverty%20and%20education%20data%20has%20exposed%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20he%20has%20overseen%20development%20in%20his%2015%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENawal%20Kishore%20Chaudhary%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20clearly%20says%20that%20Bihar%20has%20poverty%20and%20unemployment.%20About%2063.74%25%20of%20families%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%20%E2%80%93%20which%20means%20they%20are%20not%20earning%20even%20Rs%20500%20daily.%20This%20means%20Bihar%20has%20acute%20poverty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20claim%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20made%20about%20development%2C%20the%20current%20data%20is%20not%20supporting%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%202021%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20Multidimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20(MPI)%20said%20that%2051.91%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Bihar%20was%20poor%2C%20the%20highest%20among%20all%20the%20states.%20While%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20took%20many%20indicators%20into%20account%2C%20the%20caste%20census%20data%20was%20based%20on%20just%20monthly%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699375142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07214142%2FF-AjAdfbYAA6UOc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnitish-kumar-socio-economic-data-caste-survey-poverty-assistance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20announced%20a%20one-time%20benefit%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20the%2094%20lakh%20families%20that%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20a%20month.%20He%20also%20declared%20plans%20to%20increase%20reservations%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs%20to%2065%25%2C%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20capped%20at%2050%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnitish-kumar-socio-economic-data-caste-survey-poverty-assistance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reliance%20Industries%20files%20for%20record%20%242.4%20billion%20rupee%20bond%20sale%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C