hief%20Minister%20was%20saying%20was%20about%20sex%20education.%20People%20become%20hesitant%20over%20this%20topic%2C%20but%20it%20is%20taught%20in%20schools%20--%20in%20science%2C%20biology.%20Children%20learn%20this.%20He%20said%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20practically%20to%20control%20the%20population.%20This%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20in%20a%20wrong%20manner%2C%20but%20as%20sex%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20later%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20has%20come%20under%20severe%20attack%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20called%20him%20the%20most%20vulgar%20leader%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20politics%20has%20not%20seen%20a%20leader%20as%20vulgar%20as%20Nitish%20Babu.%20His%20mind%20is%20infested%20with%20the%20worms%20from%20%26quot%3BB%26quot%3B%20grade%20adult%20films.%20His%20double-meaning%20comments%20should%20be%20banned.%20Seems%20he%20has%20been%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20the%20company%20he%20keeps%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20its%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNitish%20Kumar%20has%20tarnished%20the%20dignity%20and%20decorum%20of%20democracy.%20His%20statement%20is%20like%20a%20roadside%20loafer%20and%20is%20anti-women...%20It%20is%20very%20shameful%20to%20make%20such%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20It%20seems%20he%20is%20mentally%20ill.%20He%20should%20resign%20and%20immediately%20consult%20a%20doctor%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20minister%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20has%20demanded%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNational%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20vehemently%20condemns%20the%20recent%20statements%20made%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20concerning%20women's%20fertility%20and%20education%20and%20linking%20it%20to%20the