ime%20polling%20booths%20established%20by%20the%20government.%20Due%20to%20a%20blanket%20boycott%20called%20by%20Maoists%2C%20most%20houses%20in%20Mokur%20and%20Silger%20were%20empty%2C%20except%20for%20little%20children%20and%20nursing%20mothers.%20While%2C%20just%2020%20km%20away%2C%20Marudbaka%20polling%20booth%20saw%20a%20no-show%2C%20around%2050%20voters%20from%20Silger%20turned%20up%20in%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20hours%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20here%20to%20cast%20a%20vote%20as%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20let%20go%20of%20the%20chance%20to%20make%20our%20voice%20heard.%20Protests%20will%20only%20work%20if%20people%20in%20the%20government%20are%20interested%20in%20listening%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banda%20Poyam%20(23)%20a%20resident%20of%20Silger%20who%20had%20come%20to%20vote%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20Poovarti%2C%20a%20village%20six%20km%20into%20the%20jungles%20from%20Silger%2C%20only%20half%20a%20dozen%20voters%2C%20including%20three%20women%20showed%20up%2C%20in%20a%20group%2C%20within%20the%20first%20hour%20of%20polling.%20Poovarti%2C%20the%20home%20of%20dreaded%20naxal%20commander%20Hidma%2C%20has%20always%20been%20a%20Maoist%20stronghold.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20them%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20use%20an%20electronic%20voting%20machine.%20Some%20of%20the%20earlier%20ones%20just%20walked%20in%20and%20walked%20out%2C%20clueless%20about%20what%20was%20to%20be%20done.%20We%20tried%20to%20instruct%20them%20from%20outside%2C%20but%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20supervise%20inside%20the%20booth.%20From%20next%20time%2C%20maybe%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20first%20hold%20some%20demonstration%20for%20the%20first%20time%20voters%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nag%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http