e%20about%20his%20experience%20with%20Vikrant%20Massey%20and%20Vidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra%2C%20his%20learnings%20and%20unlearnings%20and%20how%20he%20has%20handled%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20his%20acting%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pramod%20Gaikwad%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Second%20Colorado%20officer%20acquitted%20in%20Elijah%20McClain%20death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699369563000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F170C4%2Fproduction%2F_131640449_gettyimages-1268393493-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67347186%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20of%20three%20officers%20to%20face%20trial%20in%20the%2023-year-old's%202019%20death%20have%20been%20found%20not%20guilty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67347186%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67347186.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67347186.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20Warns%20Of%20%26quot%3BUnpalatable%20Decision%26quot%3B%20For%20Centre%20Amid%20Appointment%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Btroublesome%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Centre%20is%20selectively%20picking%2C%20choosing%20and%20appointing%20judges%20whose%20names%20were%20recommended%20by%20the%20collegium%20for%20appointment%20to%20the%20higher%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20also%20expressed%20its%20concern%20over%20the%20pendency%20of%20names%20recommended%20for%20transfer%20from%20one%20high%20court%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...We%20hope%20that%20a%20situation%20would%20not%20come%20where%20this%20court%20or%20the%20collegium%20have%20to%20take%20some%20decision%20which%20may%20not%20be%20palatable%20(to%20the%20government)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20two%20pleas%20including%20one%20alleging%20delay%20by%20the%20Centre%20in%20clearing%20the%20names%20recommended%20by%20the%20collegium%20for%20appointment%20and%20transfer%20of%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20also%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20names%2C%20recommended%20by%20the%20collegium%2C%20pending%20with%20the%20government%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20put%20to%20the%20Attorney%20General%20that%20this%20is%20again%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20as%20emphasized%20on%20numerous%20occasions%20that%20if%20some%20appointments%20are%20made%20and%20some%20are%20not%2C%20the%20inter-se%20seniority%20is%20disturbed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20hardly%20conducive%20to%20persuade%20successful%20lawyers%20to%20join%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20also%20appreciated%20that%20some%20appointment%20process%20was%20expedited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20pick%20and%20choose%20has%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20do%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSelectively%20picking%2C%20choosing%20and%20appointing%20is%20the%20troublesome%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kaul%20told%20Attorney%20General%20R%20Venkataramani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20this%20pick%20and%20choose%20affects%20the%20seniority%20of%20those%20whose%20names%20have%20been%20recommended%20for%20appointment%20by%20the%20collegium%20and%20why%20a%20person%2C%20having%20reasonable%20practice%20a%20as%20lawyer%2C%20would%20put%20his%20neck%20on%20the%20block%20and%20hope%20that%20the%20government%20will%20clear%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20transfer%2C%20it%20said%20whether%20a%20judge%20should%20work%20in%20a%20high%20court%20or%20other%20high%20court%20should%20be%20left%20to%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20on%20individuals.%20I%20am%20saying%20transfer%20should%20take%20place%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kaul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20the%20court%20has%20given%20a%20long%20rope%20to%20the%20government%20on%20this%20issue%20and%20there%20were%20instances%20where%20reiteration%20of%20names%20was%20done%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20your%20lordships%20to%20crack%20the%20whip%20otherwise%20the%20government%20is%20getting%20the%20impression%20that%20it%20can%20do%20away%20with%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20court%20may%20summon%20the%20law%20secretary%20for%20contempt%20otherwise%20it%20will%20never%20be%20sorted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20expressed%20our%20concern%20to%20the%20Attorney%20General%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20progress%20since%20the%20last%20date.%20The%20pendency%20of%20transfer%20matter%20is%20an%20issue%20of%20great%20concern%20as%20it%20has%20been%20selectively%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20Venkataramani%20had%20submitted%20that%20he%20was%20taking%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20observed%20that%20in%20the%20recommendations%20even%20recently%20made%2C%20selective%20appointments%20have%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20the%20Attorney%20General%20has%20requested%20time%20to%20have%20a%20fruitful%20discussion%20on%20these%20issues%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20October%2020%2C%20the%20court%20had%20flagged%20the%20pendency%20of%2021%20names%20recommended%20by%20its%20collegium%20for%20appointment%20and%20transfer%20of%20high%20court%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20told%20the%20Centre%20that%20the%20tendency%20to%20%26quot%3Bpick%20and%20choose%26quot%3B%20was%20creating%20a%20lot%20of%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20judges%20through%20the%20collegium%20system%20has%20often%20become%20a%20major%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20with%20the%20mechanism%20drawing%20criticism%20from%20different%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20hearing%20the%20petitions%2C%20including%20the%20one%20filed%20by%20the%20Advocates%20Association%20Bengaluru%20seeking%20contempt%20action%20against%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20and%20Justice%20for%20allegedly%20not%20adhering%20to%20the%20timeline%20set%20by%20the%20court%20in%20a%202021%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20pleas%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bwilful%20disobedience%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20time%20frame%20laid%20down%20in%20its%20April%2020%2C%202021%20order%20to%20facilitate%20the%20timely%20appointment%20of%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20order%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20the%20Centre%20should%20appoint%20judges%20within%20three-four%20weeks%20if%20the%20collegium%20reiterates%20its%20recommendations%20unanimously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699369380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-centres-pick-and-choose-in-appointing-judges-troublesome-4554647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20it%20