l%20Mendis%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20the%20team%20directly%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20avoiding%20the%20customary%20handshake%20with%20the%20Bangladesh%20players.%20As%20Mathews%20complained%20about%20Shakib%20and%20his%20team's%20decision%20to%20appeal%20for%20'timed%20out'%2C%20a%20reporter%20questioned%20his%20the%20Lankans'%20behaviour%20after%20they%20avoided%20the%20handshake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReporter%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20spoke%20about%20the%20Bangladesh%20players'%20behaviour%20being%20absolutely%20not%20on.%20What%20about%20the%20behaviour%20of%20your%20own%20players%2C%20refusing%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20the%20opposition%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAngelo%20Mathews%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYeah%2C%20you%20need%20to%20respect%20people%20who%20respect%20us.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20-%20they%20have%20to%20respect%20the%20game%20itself.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20all%20are%20ambassadors%20of%20this%20beautiful%20game%2C%20including%20the%20umpires.%20So%20then%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20respect%20and%20if%20you%20don't%20use%20your%20common%20sense%2C%20what%20more%20can%20you%20ask%20for%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20clarity%20on%20dismissals%20like%20this%2C%20obstructing%20the%20field%2C%20etc.%2C%20Mathews%20said%20that%20the%20rules%20are%20clear%20but%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20'common%20sense'%20over%20certain%20dismissals%2C%20as%20in%20his%20case%2C%20it%20was%20the%20helmet%20issue%20that%20resulted%20in%20a%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20think%20in%20terms%20of%20Mankading%20and%2C%20say%2C%20obstructing%20the%20field%2C%20the%20rules%20are%20quite%20clear.%20I%20mean%2C%20because%20the%20rule%20clearly%20says%20that%20if%20you're%20out%20of%20your%20crease%2C%20the%20bowler%20can%20break%20the%20stumps.%20So%2C%20if%20you're%20in%20line%20of%20the%20stumps%20and%20if%20you're%20obstructing%20the%20ball%20being%20hit%20to%20the%20stumps%2C%20then%20it%20clearly%20s