0solar%20atmosphere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20in%20a%20release%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BFlares%20produce%20enhanced%20emission%20in%20all%20wavelengths%20across%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20-%20radio%2C%20optical%2C%20UV%2C%20soft%20X-rays%2C%20hard%20X-rays%20and%20gamma-rays.%20Flare%20emission%20consists%20of%20emissions%20from%20accelerated%20particles%20and%20hot%20plasma.%20Though%20solar%20flares%20have%20been%20studied%20in%20X-rays%20and%20gamma-rays%20for%20decades%2C%20the%20initial%20impulsive%20emission%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20characterise%20and%20understand.%20The%20impulsive%20hard%20X-ray%20emission%20has%20multiple%20spectral%20components%20which%20are%20highly%20time%20variable.%20HEL1OS%20aims%20to%20overcome%20these%20difficulties%20by%20having%20a%20set%20of%20detectors%20specifically%20tuned%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20energy%20ranges%20and%20also%20provides%20very%20high%20spectral%20and%20time%20resolution%20measurements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISRO%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BCommissioned%20on%20October%2027%2C%202023%2C%20HEL1OS%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20fine-tuning%20of%20thresholds%20and%20calibration%20operations.%20The%20instrument%20is%20set%20to%20monitor%20the%20Sun's%20high-energy%20X-ray%20activity%20with%20fast%20timing%20and%20high-resolution%20spectra.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHEL1OS%20data%20enables%20researchers%20to%20study%20explosive%20energy%20release%20and%20electron%20acceleration%20during%20impulsive%20phases%20of%20solar%20flares%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAditya-L1%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%20HEL1OS%20captures%20first%20High-Energy%20X-ray%20glimpse%20of%20Solar%20Flares%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%F0%9F%94%B8During%20its%20first%20observation%20period%20from%20approximately%2012%3A00%20to%2022%3A00%20UT%20on%20October%2029%2C%202023%2C%20the%20High%20Energy%20L1%20Orbiting%20X-ray%20Spectrometer%20(HEL1OS)%20on%20board%20Aditya-L1%20has%20recorded%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FX6R9zhdwM5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FX6R9zhdwM5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1721871906851397798%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20said%20that%20HEL1OS%20was%20developed%20by%20the%20Space%20Astronomy%20Group%20of%20the%20U%20R%20Rao%20Satellite%20Centre%2C%20ISRO%2C%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20spacecraft%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%20remote%20observations%20of%20the%20solar%20corona%20and%20in-situ%20observations%20of%20the%20solar%20wind%20at%20L1%20(Sun-Earth%20Lagrangian%20point)%2C%20which%20is%20about%201.5%20million%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20dedicated%20Indian%20space%20mission%20for%20observations%20of%20the%20Sun.%20Aimed%20at%20studying%20the%20Sun%20from%20an%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%2C%20the%20mission%20carries%20seven%20payloads%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20the%20corona%2C%20in%20different%20wavebands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20is%20a%20fully%20indigenous%20effort%20with%20the%20participation%20of%20national%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20ISRO%20scientist%20told%20PTI%20that%20capturing%20the%20first%20High-Energy%20X-ray%20glimpse%20of%20Solar%20Flares%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20the%20mission%20is%20doing%20well%20on%20the%20expected%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699368420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F5431esu4_aditya-l1-19-sept_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com