ty%20prescribed%20her%20a%20sentence%20of%20isolation.%20But%20Lalitha%20did%20not%20let%20this%20define%20her%20life%20or%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332994%2Fshraddha-gaikwad-pune-security-guard-daughter-won-gold-in-skateboarding-national-level%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20choices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20her%20daughter%2C%20Syamala%20Chenulu%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20father%20passed%20away%2C%20my%20mother%20had%20to%20suffer%20more%20than%20she%20should%20have.%20Her%20mother-in-law%20had%20lost%20her%2016th%20child%20and%20took%20out%20that%20frustration%20on%20the%20young%20widow.%20It%20was%20a%20coping%20mechanism%20and%20today%2C%20I%20understand%20what%20she%20was%20going%20through.%20However%2C%20my%20mother%20decided%20not%20to%20succumb%20to%20societal%20pressures.%20She%20educated%20herself%20and%20earned%20a%20respectable%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lalitha%20chose%20the%20engineering%20path%20in%201940%2C%20she%20was%20the%20only%20female%20among%20hundreds%20of%20boys%20at%20the%20college.%20But%20she%20was%20soon%20joined%20by%20two%20other%20women%2C%20PK%20Thresia%20and%20Leelamma%20George%20Koshie%2C%20who%20also%20carved%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincredible%20niches%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20profession.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20PK%20Thresia%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lalitha%20expressed%20her%20wish%20to%20join%20the%20four-year%20engineering%20program%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Guindy%2C%20University%20of%20Madras%2C%20her%20father%20who%20was%20a%20pro