nology-67343550%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67343550.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67343550.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Need%20Proper%20Guidelines%20for%20Seizure%20of%20Digital%20Devices%20of%20Journalists%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%207%2C%20said%20there%20need%20to%20be%20proper%20guidelines%20for%20the%20seizure%20of%20digital%20devices%20of%20journalists%20to%20prevent%20misuse%20by%20investigating%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-guidelines-search-seizure-digital-devices-241799%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20made%20this%20observation%20while%20hearing%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20seeking%20safeguards%20against%20%E2%80%9Cunreasonable%20interference%E2%80%9D%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20creating%20comprehensive%20guidelines%20for%20the%20search%20and%20seizure%20of%20digital%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professional%2C%20which%20was%20represented%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Siddharth%20Agarwal.%20He%20told%20the%20court%20about%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20issues%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthreats%20that%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%E2%80%99%20unmitigated%20search%20and%20seizure%20powers%20posed%20to%20constitutional%20guarantees%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20journalists%20whose%20digital%20devices%20are%20taken%20away%20en%20masse.%20The%20issues%20raised%20in%20this%20petition%20are%20very%20significant%20because%20there%20are%20no%20guidelines%20with%20reference%20to%20when%20and%20what%20may%20be%20seized%2C%20what%20can%20be%20accessed%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20protection%20is%20ensured%20for%20personal%20data%2C%20health%20data%2C%20financial%20data%E2%80%A6%20The%20entire%20digital%20footprint%20is%20on%20that%20one%20device%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20raids%20on%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20devices%20of%20several%20journalists%20were%20seized.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fweeks-after-unprecedented-raids-newsclick-staffers-grapple-with-waiting-game%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20250%20devices%20were%20seized%20from%2090%20journalists%2C%20and%20none%20of%20them%20were%20given%20the%20mandatory%20hash%20values%20of%20their%20electronic%20items%2C%20as%20prescribed%20by%20the%20courts.%20The%20hash%20value%20defines%20how%20much%20data%20is%20on%20a%20digital%20device%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20seizure%2C%20so%20that%20any%20possible%20tampering%20is%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20solicitor%20general%20S.V.%20Raju%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20complicated%2C%20legal%20issues%20that%20are%20required%20to%20be%20examined%E2%80%9D%20and%20sought%20an%20adjournment%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20agreed%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20have%20guidelines%20that%20protect%20journalists%20from%20arbitrary%20seizures.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20serious%20matter.%20These%20are%20media%20professionals%20who%20will%20have%20their%20own%20sources%20and%20other%20things.%20There%20must%20be%20some%20guidelines.%20If%20you%20take%20everything%20away%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem.%20You%20must%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20some%20guidelines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20ASG%20Raju%20said%20that%20the%20investigating%20agency%20cannot%20be%20shut%20out%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20and%20totally%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20judge%20said%20that%C2%A0guidelines%20were%20required%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20agency%20were%20not%20misused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr%20Raju%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20finding%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20accept%20some%20kind%20of%20all-within%20power%20that%20the%20agencies%20have%E2%80%A6This%20is%20very%20dangerous.%20You%20must%20have%20better%20guidelines.%20If%20you%20want%20us%20to%20do%20it%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20do%20it.%20But%20my%20view%20is%20that%20you%20ought%20to%20do%20it%20yourself.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20you%20ensure%20that%20this%20is%20not%20misused.%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20State%20that%E2%80%99s%20run%20only%20through%20its%20agencies.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20give%20you%20time%2C%20no%20difficulty.%20But%20you%20must%20analyse%20what%20kind%20of%20guidelines%20are%20necessary%20to%20protect%20them.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20this%20is%20not%20adversarial%20in%20that%20sense%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-making-a-mockery-of-landmark-privacy-ruling%5C%22%3EDevice%20Seizures%20Are%20Making%20a%20Mockery%20of%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Landmark%20Privacy%20Ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Agarwal%20said%20the%20issue%20is%20about%20state%20power%20against%20individual%20rights%2C%20noting%20that%20investigating%20agencies%20are%20compelling%20people%20to%20provide%20biometric%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20used%20by%20all%20political%20dispensations%2C%20not%20any%20particular%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20to%20which%20Justice%20Kaul%20responded%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9COne%20dispensation%20teaches%20the%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20pronounced%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLearned%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20requests%20for%20some%20time%20to%20better%20examine%20the%20matter%20so%20that%20he%20can%20make%20submissions.%20We%20have%20however%20put%20to%20the%20learned%20ASG%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20balancing%20of%20interests%20and%20proper%20guidelines%20need%20to%20be%20in%20place%20to%20protect%20the%20interest%20of%20media%20professionals.%20We%20would%20like%20the%20learned%20ASG%20to%20work%20on%20this%20and%20come%20back%20on%20this%20issue.%20This%20is%20more%20so%20in%20view%20of%20the%20aspect%20that%20privacy%20is%20held%20to%20be%20a%20fundamental%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20will%20continue%20on%20December%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20court%20ordered%20the%20Delhi%20police%20to%20return%20the%20electronic%20devices%20seized%20from%20staffers%20of%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20almost%20a%20year%20after%20the%20crime%20branch%20conducted%20raids%20at%20its%20office%20in%20a%20defamation%20case.%20The%20court%20said%20that%20keeping%20the%20devices%20of%20journalists%20seized%20for%20long%20periods%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-journalists-seized-press-freedom-delhi-court-the-wire%5C%22%3Eimpinges%20on%20press%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20court%20rejected%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20the%20devices%20may%20be%20needed%20for%20subsequent%20investigation%20is%20%E2%80%9Cspeculative%20in%20nature%20based%20on%20the%20presumption%20of%20coming%20to%20light%20some%20new%20fact%20at%20a%20later%20stage%2C%20which%20may%20or%20may%20not%20happen%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699365503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fproper-gui