the%20Jubilee%20Hills%20constituency%20in%20Hyderabad%20this%20time%20around%2C%20where%20former%20cricketer%20Mohammad%20Azharuddin%20is%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20candidate.%20The%20party%20has%20so%20far%20declared%20six%20candidates.%20In%20the%20outgoing%20Telangana%20assembly%2C%20it%20has%20seven%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOwaisi%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20perception%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20stock%20increasing%20in%20Telangana%20will%20not%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20community.%20He%20says%20the%20minority%20community%20will%20rally%20behind%20the%20BRS%20and%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20votes%20getting%20divided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20Muslims%20are%20concerned%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20will%20be%20the%20scenario.%20People%20who%20create%20this%20argument%20cite%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20is%20different%20from%20Telangana.%20Unlike%20Karnataka%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20mob%20lynchings%2C%20beef%20bans%2C%20or%20communal%20riots%20here%20%5Bin%20Telangana%5D%2C%20and%20women%20have%20not%20been%20stopped%20from%20wearing%20hijab%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Ftelangana-model-of-peace-and-progress-must-be-adopted-everywhere-owaisi%2Farticle67501775.ece%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-muslim-voters-dilemma-congress-brs%5C%22%3EBRS%20or%20Congress%3A%20The%20Dilemma%20Facing%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20Voters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIMIM%20chief%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20nearly%20ten-year%20tenure%20of%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20has%20been%20that%20of%20communal%20amity%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20the%20Telangana%20model%20of%20governance%20should%20be%20promoted.%20%E2%80%9CTelangana%20model%20which%20is%20of%20peace%2C%20progress%2C%20prosperity%2C%20Muslim%20upliftment%20and%20communal%20amity%2C%20should%20be%20adopted%20by%20everyone.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20had%20curfew%20only%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmost-people-arrested-in-bhainsa-violence-linked-to-hindu-vahini-telangana-police%5C%22%3EBhainsa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20overall%20it%20has%20been%20very%20peaceful.%20You%20have%20a%20Hindu%20chief%20minister%20whose%20practicing%20of%20faith%20is%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20anyone.%20This%20government%20has%20spent%20about%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%20for%20the%20upkeep%20of%20temples.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20some%2017%2C000%20imams%20and%20muezzins%20are%20paid%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOwaisi%20dismissed%20the%20allegation%20that%20both%20BRS%20and%20AIMIM%20are%20in%20an%20understanding%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20The%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20has%20been%20alleging%20that%20the%20three%20parties%20are%20in%20cahoots%2C%20and%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Clenient%E2%80%9D%20towards%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20government%20despite%20corruption%20allegations.%20As%20for%20the%20AIMIM%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20accusing%20it%20of%20helping%20the%20BJP%20indirectly%20by%20fielding%20candidates%20across%20Muslim-dominated%20constituencies%20in%20the%20country%20to%20split%20the%20anti-BJP%20vote.%20It%20was%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvoter-cutter%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%20The%20party%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20Rajasthan%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHad%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20pressure%20been%20here%20%5Bin%20Telangana%5D%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20communal%20riots.%20How%20is%20it%20that%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20minorities%20in%20nine%20years%3F%20The%20Muslim%20representation%20in%20Shaadi%20Mubarak%20and%20Kalyana%20Lakshmi%20schemes%20is%2021.23%25.%20In%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20BC%2C%20and%20Minorities%20overseas%20scholarship%2C%20the%20minority%20share%20is%2047.26%25.%20The%20total%20budget%20for%20Kalyana%20Lakshmi%2C%20Shaadi%20Mubarak%2C%20ST%2C%20SC%2C%20BC%2C%20Minorities%20overseas%20scholarship%2C%20residential%20schools%2C%20etc.%2C%20is%20Rs%2091%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20the%20share%20of%20minorities%2013.18%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Owaisi%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20counter%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-elections%2Ftelangana-polls-2023-asaduddin-owaisi-led-aimim-takes-money-from-bjp-to-claims-rahul-gandhi-11698847471176.html%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20AIMIM%20fields%20candidates%20by%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20money%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20BJP%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20contest%20between%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20came%20after%20AIMIM%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20field%20candidates%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20mostly%20in%20Muslim-majority%20seats.%20The%20Hyderabad-based%20party%20has%20so%20far%20announced%20candidates%20for%20the%20Hawa%20Mahal%20seat%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20Fatehpur%20in%20Sikar%2C%20and%20Kaman%20in%20Bharatpur%20%E2%80%93%20all%20currently%20held%20by%20the%20Congress.%20The%20party%20is%20expected%20to%20announce%20candidates%20for%20more%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOwaisi%20flatly%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20Gandhi%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20his%20party%20had%20supported%20the%20nuclear%20deal%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20government%2C%20backed%20Congress%20candidates%20for%20president%2C%20and%20threw%20its%20weight%20behind%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Kiran%20Kumar%20Reddy%20in%20the%20united%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20when%20he%20faced%20a%20no-confidence%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWas%20money%20given%20to%20me%20then%3F%20If%20everything%20is%20about%20money%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20then%20I%20can%20also%20ask%20if%20Modi%20gave%20him%20money%20so%20that%20Congress%20is%20reduced%20to%2040-%20or%2050-odd%20seats%20in%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Owaisi%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fasaduddin-owaisi-rahul-gandhi-telangana-elections-101698990152262.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CRahul%20Gandhi%2C%20you%20make%20these%20accusations%20because%20my%20name%20is%20Asaduddin.%20Because%20I%20have%20a%20beard%20on%20my%20face%20and%20wear%20%5Ba%5D%20skull%20cap%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20you%20make%20allegations%20of%20taking%20money%20against%20me%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20He%20told%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20your%20hatred%20against%20this%20name%20and%20you%20have%20hatred%20against%20those%20donning%20beard%20and%20skull%20cap.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20you%20make%20the%20allegations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20ruled%20out%20a%20fractured%20mandate%20in%20Telangana%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cintentions%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20possible%20coalition%20government%20in%20the%20state%20would%20not%20come%20true.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20fractured%20mandate.%20BRS%20will%20get%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%20%3Ci%3E%3C%2Fi%3EA%20coalition%20government%20is%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20BJP.%20B.L.%20Santhosh%2C%20who%20came%20from%20the%20RSS%2C%20said%20that%20no%20party%20would%20get%20a%20majority.%20This%20shows%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20intentions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20November%2030%2C%20and%20the%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20December%203.%20The%20BRS%20is%20facing