ders%20or%20those%20who%20have%20switched%20over%20to%20its%20camp%20from%20other%20parties%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20often%20than%20not%2C%20it%20is%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20reveal%20details%20about%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20actions%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%20Even%20as%20the%20agency%20conducts%20raids%20without%20divulging%20many%20details%20about%20the%20charges%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20reveal%20them%20to%20the%20press.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20evident%20in%20the%20cases%20against%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leaders%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case%2C%20and%20also%20with%20Baghel.%20The%20BJP%20first%20released%20the%20video%20in%20which%20the%20suspect%20named%20Baghel.%20The%20ED%20issued%20a%20press%20release%20naming%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20only%20later.%20Congress%20leaders%20said%20the%20BJP%20amplified%20the%20charges%20against%20Baghel%20much%20more%20than%20the%20ED%20%E2%80%93%20a%20phenomenon%20that%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20called%20%E2%80%9Ca%20clear-cut%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20to%20tarnish%20Baghel%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20approaches%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20a%20context%2C%20the%20Congress%20highlighted%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fmadhya-pradesh-assembly%2Fcongress-calls-for-action-over-video-of-narendra-tomars-son-discussing-money-transactions%2Farticle67504887.ece%5C%22%3Ealleged%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20purported%20representatives%20of%20mining%20companies%2C%20directing%20them%20to%20transfer%20crores%20of%20rupees%20to%20different%20bank%20accounts.%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20demanded%20that%20the%20ED%20should%20also%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20same%20urgency%20in%20which%20Baghel%20was%20named%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20probe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clip%2C%20just%20over%20six%20minutes%2C%20allegedly%20shows%20Devendra%20and%20another%20person%20speaking%20about%20someone%20called%20%E2%80%98Tyagi%E2%80%99%20who%20could%20give%20Rs%20100%20crore%20through%20a%20retired%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20commissioner.%20However%2C%20the%20other%20person%20says%20that%20the%20deal%20has%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98finalised%E2%80%99%20first.%20Then%20they%20speak%20about%20financial%20transactions%20with%20one%20Harpreet%20Gill.%20Devendra%E2%80%99s%20father%20Tomar%20is%20contesting%20the%20assembly%20elections%20from%20the%20Dimani%20seat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07182413%2FFvSww3facAAB0wX.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07182413%2FFvSww3facAAB0wX.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07182413%2FFvSww3facAAB0wX-300x165.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07182413%2FFvSww3facAAB0wX-1024x562.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683964%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22659%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDevendra%20Pratap%20Singh%20Tomar.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40DevendraPSTomar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20asked%20whether%20the%20ED%20or%20the%20BJP%20will%20act%20similarly%20after%20a%20video%20purportedly%20showed%20Union%20minister%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20Devendra%20Pratap%20Singh%20Tomar%20discussing%20funds%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20100%20crore%20with%20a%20man%20alleged%20to%20be%20representing%20the%20mining%20lobby.%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20the%20ED%20have%20remained%20tight-lipped%20about%20the%20video%2C%20even%20as%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20the%20clip.%20Devendra%20Pratap%20claimed%20that%20the%20clip%20was%20doctored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20has%20demanded%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20and%20called%20for%20the%20Union%20minister%20to%20step%20aside%20until%20the%20probe%20is%20complete.%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20is%20a%20powerful%20man%20not%20just%20in%20Delhi%2C%20but%20also%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20A%20free%20and%20fair%20investigation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20possible%20until%20his%20son%20is%20arrested%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shrinate%20said.%20Other%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20Kamal%20Nath%20demanded%20an%20inquiry%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%2C%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20against%20Tomar%20and%20asked%20the%20agencies%20to%20immediately%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShrinate%20said%20that%20since%20the%20discussion%20is%20about%20five%20different%20bank%20accounts%20for%20alleged%20funding%2C%20the%20video%20should%20immediately%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20person%20in%20conversation%20with%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20spoke%20about%20Krishna%20Menon%20Marg%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20the%20Union%20minister%20also%20stays.%20She%20said%20the%20matter%20is%20extremely%20significant%20as%20Tomar%20was%20the%20minister%20of%20mines%20and%20iron%20ore%20in%20the%20Modi%20cabinet%20before%20his%20term%20as%20agriculture%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20media%20coordinator%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Piyush%20Babele%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDear%20ED%2C%20CBI%2C%20Income%20Tax%2C%20this%20video%20is%20going%20viral.%20Please%20check%20its%20authenticity.%20In%20this%20video%2C%20BJP%20candidate%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20Devendra%20Tomar%20seems%20to%20be%20discussing%20transactions%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees.%20Please%20investigate%20and%20clarify%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20black%20money%20or%20white%20money%20in%20between%20the%20model%20code%20code%20of%20conduct.%20(sic)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20both%20parties%20locking%20horns%20over%20the%20charges%20against%20Baghel%20and%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20the%20Congress%20sought%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Bhopal%20and%20also%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20possible%20illegal%20financing%20of%20elections%20by%20the%20BJP%20leader.%20However%2C%20the%20ECI%20told%20the%20Congress%20that%20it%20was%20busy%20and%20could%20meet%20only%20after%20polling%20concludes%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leader%2C%20told%20the%20press%20that%20the%20party%20wanted%20the%20ECI%20to%20take%20note%20of%20the%20video%20and%20also%20%E2%80%9Cban%20the%20objectionable%20statements%20of%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20are%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20disrupting%20the%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20definitely%20an%20attempt%20to%20obstruct%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20definitely%20an%20attempt%20to%20muddy%20the%20field%20because%20the%20BJP%20knows%20that%20they%20are%20losing%20badly%2C%20it%20is%20definitely%20an%20attempt%20to%20paint%20a%20black%20picture%20where%20they%20know%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E%20realise%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%E2%80%99s%20press%20notes%20levelling%20all%20sorts%20of%20allegations%20went%20against%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20providing%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20to%20all%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20ED%20%E2%80%9Cappeared%20to%20be%20working%20in%20close%20coordination%2C%20as%20first%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20that%20issues%20a%20video%2C%20which%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20press%20release%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699362323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-ed-contrasting-approach-bhupesh-baghel-devendra-tomar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20urgency%20with%20which%20the%20agency%20accused%20the%20Chattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20of%20receiving%20money%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20case%2C%20based%20a%20video%20from%20a%20primary%20accused%2C%20has%20been%20contrasted%20with%20its%20silence%20on%20a%20video%20allegedly%20showing%20Devendra%20Pratap%20Singh%20Tomar%20discussing%20the%20transfer%20of%20funds%20with%20a%20representative%20of%20mining%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-ed-contrasting-approach-bhupesh-baghel-devendra-tomar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Rights%20Groups%20Urge%20FATF%20to%20Call%20on%20the%20Indian%20Govt%20to%20Stop%20Alleged%20UAPA%2C%20PMLA%2C%20FCRA%20Abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19225020%2F332105462_903328324039187_7204366883760295212_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Recognising%20the%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20terror%20laws%20in%20India%2C%20several%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20have%20urged%20the%20global%20terrorism%20financing%20and%20money%20laundering%20watchdog%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fatf-gafi.org%2Fen%2Fthe-fatf%2Fwhat-we-do.html%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20call%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20stop%20prosecuting%2C%20intimidating%20and%20harassing%20human%20rights%20defenders%20and%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Bar%20Association%20Centre%20for%20Human%20Rights%20released%20a%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20adverse%20impact%20of%20counter%20terrorism%20laws%20on%20human%20rights%20defenders%20and%20FATF%20compliance%E2%80%99%2C%20analysing%20India%E2%80%99s%20three%20major%20terror%20and%20money%20laundering%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20and%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20three%20rights%20organisations%20%E2%80%93%20Amnesty%20International%2C%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20Security%20Network%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20have%20pointed%20to%20the%20exploitative%20nature%20of%20the%20terror%20and%20money%20laundering%20laws%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20organisations%20have%20accused%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20restricting%20civic%20space%20and%20stifling%20the%20rights%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20association%20and%20peaceful%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDraconian%20laws%20introduced%20or%20adapted%20to%20this%20end%20include%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%20(FCRA)%2C%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20and%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%20Their%20actions%20have%20flouted%20both%20FATF%E2%80%99s%20standards%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20group%20claims%20in%20their%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Bar%20Association%2C%20in%20its%2065-%20page%20statement%2C%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20non-compliance%20of%20the%20FATF%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20report%20finds%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20counter-terrorism%20laws%20have%20expanded%20over%20time%2C%20becoming%20increasingly%20vague%2C%20and%20often%20overturning%20basic%20procedural%20safeguards%20for%20defendants%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnewsclick-case-if-modi-government-is-really-serious-about-terror-financing-why-havent-they-rung-the-us-china-and-fatf%5C%22%3ENewsClick%20Case%3A%20If%20Modi%20Govt%20is%20Really%20Serious%20About%20%E2%80%98Terror%20Financing%E2%80%99%2C%20Why%20Hasn%E2%80%99t%20It%20Rung%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20FATF%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20joined%20the%20FATF%2C%20an%20intergovernmental%20body%20comprising%2040%20member%20countries%20that%20is%20mandated%20to%20tackle%20money%20laundering%2C%20terrorist%20financing%20and%20other%20threats%20to%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20global%20financial%20system%2C%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20year%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20itself%20had%20recognised%20the%20risk%20posed%20by%20the%20non-profit%20sector%20as%20%E2%80%9Clow%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20rights%20organisations%20say%20that%20things%20changed%20since%20the%20BJP%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20authorities%20have%20used%20overbroad%20provisions%20in%20domestic%20law%20to%20silence%20critics%20and%20shut%20down%20their%20operations%2C%20including%20by%20cancelling%20their%20foreign%20funding%20licenses%20and%20prosecuting%20them%20using%20counterterrorism%20law%20and%20financial%20regulations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20were%20compiled%20and%20presented%20days%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-fatf-meeting-report-says-india-weaponising-terror-financing-money-laundering-laws-against-ngos%5C%22%3EFATF%E2%80%99s%20Mutual%20Evaluation%20Review%20(MER)%3C%2Fa%3E%20concluded%20on%20November%203.%20The%20MER%20was%20to%20evaluate%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20laws%20and%20the%20financing%20of%20terrorism%20in%20India%20and%20the%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Bar%20Association%20has%20pointed%20to%20five%20different%20case%20studies%20from%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Felgar-parishad%5C%22%3EElgar%20Parishad%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20journalist%20Siddique%20Kappan%E2%80%99s%20cases%2C%20to%20show%20how%20terror%20laws%20have%20been%20misused%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20dissenting%20voices%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Bar%20Association%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20case%20of%20journalist%20Siddique%20Kappan%20and%20his%20co-accused%20%E2%80%93%20of%20whom%2C%20two%20are%20student%20activists%2C%20and%20another%20a%20taxi%20driver%20%E2%80%93%20is%20one%20of%20the%20starkest%20illustrations%20of%20the%20misuse%20of%20terror%20funding%20laws%20for%20political%20means.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKappan%20was%20in%20prison%20for%20over%20two%20years%20from%20October%205%2C%202020%2C%20facing%20multiple%20charges%20under%20the%20UAPA%20and%20the%20PMLA.%20He%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20journalist%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20arrest%2C%20he%20served%20as%20a%20contributing%20reporter%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fazhimugham.com%5C%22%3EMalayalam-language%20online%20portal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20also%20secretary%20of%20the%20Delhi%20chapter%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Union%20of%20Working%20Journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FRENK9-VKWMI%3Fsi%3Dn3zvd7JQfAOElx22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20Kappan%20was%20sharing%20a%20taxi%20with%20two%20others%20to%20follow%20up%20on%20a%20story%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fhathras-gang-rape-and-murder-case-a-timeline%5C%22%3EHathras%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20a%20Dalit%20woman%20was%20raped.%20She%20later%20succumbed%20to%20her%20injuries%20in%20a%20Delhi%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKappan%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20insisted%20that%20his%20low-paying%20employment%20and%20lack%20of%20proficiency%20in%20the%20local%20language%20(Hindi)%20forced%20him%20to%20share%20a%20taxi%20with%20two%20others%20who%20were%20also%20travelling%20to%20Hathras%20to%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20before%20they%20could%20reach%20Hathras%2C%20the%20three%20passengers%20and%20the%20driver%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20and%20a%20petty%20case%20of%20breach%20of%20peace%20was%20filed%20against%20them.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20another%20first%20information%20report%20invoking%20far%20graver%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20UAPA%20were%20registered%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKappan%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fi-was-targeted-because-i-am-a-muslim-siddique-kappan-recounts-his-harrowing-time-in-jail%5C%22%3Eprolonged%20incarceration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20came%20to%20an%20end%20on%20September%209%2C%202022%2C%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20him%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20oral%20observations%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20raised%20serious%20questions%20over%20the%20prosecution%E2%80%99s%20case%20that%20Kappan%20and%20others%20had%20planned%20to%20incite%20violence.%20Responding%20specifically%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20that%20%E2%80%9Cprovocative%E2%80%9D%2