Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20event%20was%20used%20to%20justify%20the%20issual%20of%20the%20draconian%20%E2%80%98Decree%20of%20the%20Reich%20President%20for%20the%20Protection%20of%20the%20People%20and%20the%20State%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fencyclopedia.ushmm.org%2Fcontent%2Fen%2Farticle%2Freichstag-fire-decree%5C%22%3Ewhich%20suspended%20civil%20liberties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Enabling%20Act%2C%20which%20concentrated%20power%20with%20Hitler%20and%20accelerated%20the%20transformation%20of%20Germany%20into%20a%20brutal%20ethno-nationalist%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2029%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20became%20excited%20when%20a%20bomb%20exploded%20at%20a%20prayer%20convention%20of%20Jehovah%E2%80%99s%20Witnesses%2C%20a%20marginal%20Christian%20sect%20in%20Kerala%2C%20that%20tragically%20killed%20four%20and%20injured%20dozens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20demography%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20frustrating%20commitment%20of%20large%20sections%20of%20Hindus%20to%20secularism%20meant%20that%2C%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20the%20Sangh%20had%20to%20attract%20Christian%20voters%20into%20their%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20Sangh%20that%20demonises%20and%20assaults%20Christians%20in%20most%20other%20regions%20in%20the%20country%20has%20nurtured%20a%20category%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EChri-sanghis%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20shrill%20and%20viscerally%20anti-Muslim%20voice%20to%20break%20the%20longstanding%20alliances%20among%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConveniently%2C%20the%20event%20also%20happened%20in%20Kalamassery%2C%20a%20pocket%20numerically%20dominated%20by%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20bombing%20tragedy%20was%20shaping%20nicely%20for%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20Reichstag%20Fire.%20It%20is%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20fascist%20movements%20to%20instil%20fear%20among%20common%20people%2C%20intimidate%20opponents%20and%20usurp%20the%20state%20machinery%20where%20electoral%20oppositions%20are%20formidable.%20They%20are%20confident%20of%20their%20proficiency%20to%20widen%20social%20cleavages%2C%20organise%20street%20violence%20and%20engineer%20communal%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20bleak%20electoral%20chances%20in%20Kerala%2C%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20was%20not%20a%20far-fetched%20hope.%20This%20was%20an%20opportunity%20they%20had%20been%20waiting%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisappointment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20Sangh%20establishment%20immediately%20swung%20into%20action%2C%20salivating%20and%20laser-focused.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vice-president%20K.S.%20Radhakrishnan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNlfeRQoR3zo%5C%22%3Erushed%20to%20note%20in%20alarmist%20tones%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Kalamassery%20has%20a%20history%20of%20extremist%20activities%20and%20demanded%20investigation%20by%20Union%20government%20agencies%20as%20the%20state%20police%20had%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESandeep%20Varier%2C%20another%20prominent%20BJP%20leader%2C%20posted%20ignorantly%20on%20Facebook%20that%20Jehovah%E2%80%99s%20Witnesses%20was%20the%20same%20as%20Judaism%2C%20and%20linked%20the%20blast%20to%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20virulent%20and%20consequential%20post%20was%20by%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20who%20posted%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDirty%20shameless%20appeasement%20politics%20by%20a%20discredited%20CM%20(and%20HM)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpinarayivijayan%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40pinarayivijayan%3C%2Fa%3E%20besieged%20by%20corruption%20charges%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20Delhi%20and%20protesting%20against%20Israel%20%2C%20when%20in%20Kerala%20open%20calls%20by%20Terrorist%20Hamas%20for%20Jihad%20is%20causing%20attacks%20and%20bomb%20blasts%20on%20innocent%20christians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMQH0ycZsqu%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMQH0ycZsqu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40Rajeev_GoI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeev_GoI%2Fstatus%2F1718561932066836946%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6QOuMxIVHmo%5C%22%3EHe%20went%20much%20further%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20blasts%20were%20directly%20linked%20to%20anti-Israel%20events%20being%20held%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20view%20spread%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20and%20reinforced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2FT53WQFaxfyw%5C%22%3Esystematic%20efforts%20underway%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Sangh%20and%20its%20affiliates%20to%20malign%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDisappointingly%20for%20the%20Sangh%2C%20the%20perpetrator%20surrendered%20within%20hours%20and%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20nothing%20of%20the%20type%20they%20wanted%20%E2%80%93%20an%20unassuming%20English%20teacher%2C%20Dominic%20Martin%2C%20who%20was%20a%20disillusioned%20member%20of%20the%20sect.%20Not%20the%20ideal%20name%20or%20profile%20for%20a%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FHWXd62WThPA%3Fsi%3D8ac7gylvpkeDRQIy%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangh%20campaign%20petered%20out%2C%20with%20many%20deleting%20their%20tweets%20and%20backtracking%20from%20their%20positions.%20As%20palpable%20as%20the%20dejection%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20was%20the%20huge%20wave%20of%20relief%20that%20swept%20over%20the%20citizens%20of%20Kerala%20and%20mainstream%20political%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20factors%20that%20contained%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20designs%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20worked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20thwarting%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20design%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20crucial.%20The%20maturity%20of%20its%20senior%20leaders%20to%20keep%20aside%20intense%20rivalries%20and%20provide%20mature%20and%20measured%20statements%20brought%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20public%20together%20against%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20V.D.%20Satheesan%2C%20when%20responding%20to%20the%20media%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mathrubhumi.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala%2Fkalamassery-blast-case-vd-satheesan-response-1.9026019%5C%22%3Eprioritised%20medical%20care%20for%20the%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20the%20government.%20He%20underlined%20that%20this%20was%20an%20issue%20to%20be%20handled%20with%20utmost%20care%20and%20warned%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20spreading%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkerala-blasts-all-party-meet-unity-hatred-suspicion-9005644%2F%5C%22%3Eall-party%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20by%20the%20government%20was%20another%20venue%20for%20the%20display%20of%20unity%20against%20polarising%20misinformation%20and%20curtailing%20the%20tensions%20being%20fuelled%20by%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20apparatuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20roasting%20that%20Chandrashekhar%20received%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Kochi%20for%20his%20communal%20statements%20was%20heartening.%20In%20these%20bleak%20times%2C%20when%20the%20media%20has%20become%20a%20lapdog%20of%20the%20regime%2C%20the%20moral%20outrage%20of%20mainstream%20journalists%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20was%20on%20full%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FC3WCGhQDGm8%3Fsi%3D6VWSCPVTJMGn7-wi%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharp%20questions%20forced%20Chandrashekhar%20to%20deny%20that%20his%20statements%20were%20communal.%20He%20tried%20in%20vain%20to%20convince%20others%20that%20his%20statement%20was%20about%20Islamic%20radicalisation%20in%20the%20state%20and%20its%20consequences%2C%20rather%20than%20related%20to%20this%20particular%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20spite%20of%20Martin%E2%80%99s%20confession%20and%20arrest%2C%20Chandrashekar%20desperately%20clung%20to%20the%20hope%20that%20future%20investigations%20would%20reveal%20an%20Islamist%20conspiracy%20and%20debunk%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnarrative%20being%20peddled%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20blast%20was%20the%20work%20of%20one%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20hard%20to%20remember%20a%20similar%20instance%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20where%20mainstream%20journalists%20held%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20present%20Union%20government%20to%20this%20level%20of%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20seriousness%20with%20which%20the%20state%20government%20dealt%20with%20the%20blast%20also%20reveals%20an%20acuity%20about%20the%20political%20climate%20and%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20capabilities%20for%20organising%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officials%20and%20ministers%20were%20dispatched%20within%20hours.%20The%20health%20minister%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%2C%20organising%20emergency%20medical%20care.%20The%20chief%20minister%2C%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20pulled%20no%20punches%20and%20accused%20Chandrashekhar%20of%20spitting%20the%20%E2%80%98poison%E2%80%99%20of%20hate.%20The%20Kerala%20police%20followed%20up%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkerala-police-fir-rajeev-chandrasekhar-tweet-blasts%5C%22%3Eregistering%20cases%20against%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20others%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Sangh%20for%20the%20incitement%20of%20riots%20and%20disruption%20of%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20absolute%20defence%20of%20secularism%2C%20intolerance%20of%20hate%20speech%20and%20the%20willingness%20to%20take%20on%20the%20Sangh%20using%20both%20political%20and%20legal%20strategies%20is%20something%20that%20other%20state%20governments%20could%20emulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Freal-kerala-story-communal-harmony-ground-zero%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Real%E2%80%99%20Kerala%20Story%3A%20Tales%20of%20Communal%20Harmony%20From%20Ground%20Zero%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20underlined%20the%20significance%20of%20vernacular%20languages%20in%20resistance.%20Some%20of%20the%20standard%20polarising%20idioms%20of%20Hindutva%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20translate%20well.%20The%20equivalent%20translations%20of%20direct%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%20perfected%20in%20Hindi%20and%20other%20northern%20Indian%20languages%20(%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EGoli%20maro%20salon%20ko%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20for%20example)%20sound%20laborious%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20that%20is%20written%20or%20spoken%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20several%20deep-rooted%20and%20trusted%20vernacular%20news%20media%20organisations%20meant%20that%20there%20was%20no%20vacuum%20for%20social%20media%2C%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20favoured%20tool%20for%20its%20propaganda%2C%20to%20fill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20the%20vernacular%20was%20on%20display%20when%20Chandrashekhar%E2%80%99s%20patchy%20grasp%20of%20Malayalam%20forced%20him%20to%20use%20broken%20phrases%20and%20wild%20gestures%20in%20the%20press%20conference%3B%20a%20stark%20disadvantage%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20majority%20of%20home-grown%20politicians%20who%20comfortably%20provide%20sophisticated%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20suggests%20that%20the%20resistance%20to%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%2C%20which%20has%20failed%20to%20take%20off%20from%20predominantly%20English-speaking%20spaces%20until%20now%2C%20maybe%20more%20effective%20when%20launched%20from%20vernacular%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20near%20miss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20event%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20warning%2C%20a%20near%20miss.%20Any%20delay%20in%20the%20surrender%20and%20arrest%20of%20the%20accused%20would%20have%20allowed%20the%20Sangh%20to%20gleefully%20wreak%20havoc.%20The%20spontaneous%20solidarity%20and%20almost%20visceral%20rejection%20of%20fascist%20designs%20by%20its%20political%20class%2C%20its%20vernacular%20media%20and%20its%20people%20helped%20Kerala%20narrowly%20dodge%20a%20cataclysm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20solidarity%20and%20alertness%20should%20be%20celebrated%20but%20also%20strengthened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala%20may%20not%20be%20the%20same%20in%20future.%20The%20next%20version%20of%20the%20Reichstag%20Fire%20can%20get%20fuelled%20into%20a%20conflagration%20that%20will%20burn%20down%20everything%20they%20value%20into%20ashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprabhir-vishnu-poruthiyil%5C%22%3EPrabhir%20Vishnu%20Poruthiyil%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20faculty%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Studies%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Bombay.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699356548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07152203%2FReichstag-fire.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkerala-blast-reichstag-fire-that-wasnt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sangh%20parivar%20became%20excited%20when%20a%20bomb%20exploded%20at%20a%20prayer%20convention%20of%20Jehovah%E2%80%99s%20Witnesses%20in%20Kerala.%20But%20the%20s