en%2Firan-teen-armita-geravand-brain-dead-after-hijab-incident%2Fa-67177851%5C%22%3Edeath%20of%2017-year-old%20Armita%20Geravand%3C%2Fa%3E%20unfortunately%20proves.%20In%20early%20October%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20school%20without%20a%20headscarf.%20After%20an%20alleged%20assault%20by%20the%20so-called%20morality%20police%20on%20the%20Tehran%20metro%2C%20the%20teenager%20fell%20unconscious%20and%20was%20hospitalized%20with%20severe%20head%20trauma.%20There%20she%20remained%20in%20a%20coma%20until%20she%20was%20declared%20brain%20dead.%20She%20was%20buried%20on%20October%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20Iranian%20women%20outraged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Iranian%20student%20from%20the%20capital%20Tehran%20told%20DW%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20risk%20our%20lives%20every%20day%20because%20we%20are%20outside%20without%20our%20headscarves.%20It%20is%20sad%20to%20see%20that%20many%20actresses%20still%20wear%20one.%E2%80%9D%20She%20pointed%20to%20the%20recent%20gathering%20of%20film%20industry%20insiders%20at%20the%20funeral%20of%20murdered%20Iranian%20director%20Dariush%20Mehrjui%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20screenwriter%20Vahideh%20Mohammadifar%2C%20on%20October%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-October%2C%20both%20had%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20with%20knife%20wounds.%20The%20movie%20industry%20and%20the%20wider%20public%20were%20shocked%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20Authorities%20spoke%20of%20a%20robbery%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20former%20gardener.%20But%20many%20remained%20skeptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20filmmakers%20in%20Iran%2C%20Mehrjui%20was%20often%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20state%20authorities.%20In%20March%202022%2C%20when%20his%20last%20film%20%E2%80%9CLa%20Minor%E2%80%9D%20was%20censored%2C%20the%2083-year-old%20posted%20an%20angry%20message%20to%20the%20Iran%20culture%20ministry%20on%20social%20media%2C%20stating%3A%20%E2%80%9CKill%20me%2C%20do%20whatever%20you%20want%20with%20me%20%E2%80%A6%20destroy%20me%2C%20but%20I%20want%20my%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20burial%2C%20many%20noteworthy%20actresses%20wore%20headscarves.%20The%20only%20woman%20to%20defy%20the%20obligatory%20hijab%20mandate%20was%2016-year-old%20Mona%20Mehrjui%2C%20the%20murdered%20couple%E2%80%99s%20daughter%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98The%20price%20of%20resistance%20is%20high%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20understand%20that%20the%20younger%20generation%20is%20angry%20with%20us.%20My%20generation%20is%20conservative%20and%20cautious%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Shole%20Pakravan%20told%20DW.%20The%20stage%20actress%20and%20author%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Germany%20since%202017.%20Three%20years%20prior%2C%20her%20daughter%20Reyhaneh%20Jabbari%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-executes-reyhaneh-jabbari-despite-international-opposition%2Fa-18020700%5C%22%3Eexecuted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Iran%20for%20killing%20the%20man%20who%20tried%20to%20rape%20her.%20Pakravan%20fought%20long%20and%20hard%20to%20save%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20life%C2%A0but%20was%20unsuccessful.%20Now%C2%A0she%20raises%20her%20voice%20for%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20right%20now%C2%A0the%20price%20of%20resistance%20in%20Iran%20is%20very%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20vanish%20out%20of%20sight%2C%20you%20must%20reluctantly%20wear%20a%20headscarf.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20resistance%20in%20Iran%20had%20ended%20though.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20changed%20and%20will%20reappear%20in%20new%20forms.%20Those%20in%20power%20can%20never%20undo%20what%20happened%20last%20year%20in%20Iran.%20They%20are%20now%20facing%20a%20young%20and%20courageous%20generation%20of%20women%20who%20know%20what%20they%20want%3A%20Freedom%20and%20the%20end%20of%20oppression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E