t%2025.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20on%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20status%20report%20has%20been%20deferred.%20The%20status%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbfsi.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findustry%2Fhindenburg-adani-matter-petitioner-seeks-early-supreme-court-hearing%2F105005543%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2022%20out%20of%2024%20investigations%20are%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court-led%20expert%20committee%20has%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20the%20matter.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20expert%20panel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fsc-appointed-panel-on-adani-group-finds-no-regulatory-failure-on-price-manipulation-report%2Farticle66869523.ece%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20point%20to%20a%20regulatory%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20raised%20concerns%20on%20the%20allegation%20of%20violation%20of%20minimum%20public%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinimum%20public%20shareholding%20or%20free%20float%20refers%20to%20the%20shares%20of%20a%20company%20that%20can%20be%20publicly%20traded%20and%20are%20not%20restricted%20(i.e.%2C%20held%20by%20insiders).%20According%20to%20SEBI%20rules%2C%20listed%20companies%20are%20required%20to%20maintain%20a%20minimum%20public%20holding%20(or%20free%20float)%20of%2025%25.%20This%20allows%20a%20company%20to%20raise%20money%20from%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFulfilling%20this%20criteria%20is%20required%20to%20stay%20listed%20on%20the%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20expert%20committee%20report%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbecause-of-repealed-provisions-sebi-hit-opaque-structure-wall-while-investigating-adani-sc-panel%5C%22%3ESEBI%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20get%20adequate%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20offshore%20funds%20because%20of%20repealed%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20offshore%20funds%2C%20whose%20ultimate%20beneficiary%20is%20unknown%2C%20because%20of%20the%20countries%E2%80%99%20tax%20haven%20status%2C%20have%20immensely%20contributed%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies.%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20columnist%20Andy%20Mukherjee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcompanies%2Fgautam-adani-and-his-fortune-drivers-deserve-keener-spotlight-scrutiny-122092300102_1.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20in%20September%202022%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20these%20%E2%80%9Csilent%20soldiers%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9CAdani%E2%80%99s%20fortune%20drivers%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20deserve%20some%20scrutiny%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20panel%20report%20said%20that%20these%20provisions%20of%20requiring%20FPIs%20to%20disclose%20%E2%80%9Cultimate%20natural%20person%E2%80%9D%20were%20done%20away%20with%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%202018%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20dealing%20with%20an%20%E2%80%98opaque%20structure%E2%80%99%20and%20requiring%20an%20FPI%20to%20disclose%20every%20ultimate%20natural%20person%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20chain%20of%20every%20owner%20of%20economic%20interest%20with%20the%20FPI%20was%20done%20away%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20regulator%20had%20even%20approached%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20for%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20documents%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-sebi-asks-occrp-for-documents%2Farticleshow%2F104510536.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20documents%20showed%20that%20SEBI%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20in%202014%20about%20alleged%20stock%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20January%202014%20DRI%20alert%20was%20sent%20to%20former%20SEBI%20chairman%20U.K.%20Sinha%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%20was%20allegedly%20siphoning%20money%20by%20overvaluing%20power%20equipment%20imports%20and%20investing%20them%20in%20listed%20companies%20via%20entities%20located%20in%20Mauritius%20and%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20network%20of%20investigative%20reporters%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsebi-occrp-documents-adani-allegations%5C%22%3Erefused%3C%2Fa%3E%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20sources%20of%20information%20are%20accessible%20through%20official%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20told%20SEBI%20that%20its%20long-standing%20policy%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20any%20documents%20beyond%20what%20is%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699348203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-chandrachud-says-hell-look-into-the-repeated-deferrals-in-sc-listing-of-adani-hindenburg-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20matter%20was%20to%20be%20listed%20on%20August%2028%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20deferred%2C%20deferred%2C%20deferred%2C'%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-chandrachud-says-hell-look-into-the-repeated-deferrals-in-sc-listing-of-adani-hindenburg-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poland%20President%20Gives%20Outgoing%20PM%20First%20Shot%20at%20Forming%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07111739%2FAndrzej-Duda-e1699336500213.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpoland%2Ft-19070837%5C%22%3EPolish%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0President%20Andrzej%20Duda%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20on%20Monday%20that%20he%20had%20asked%20outgoing%20Prime%20Minister%20Mateusz%20Morawiecki%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Flaw-and-justice-pis%2Ft-66789976%5C%22%3Ethe%20ruling%20PiS%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20try%20to%20form%20a%20new%20government%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpoland-election-tusks-opposition-alliance-secures-majority%2Fa-67117296%5C%22%3Eafter%20October%E2%80%99s%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20calm%20analysis%20and%20consultations%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20entrust%20the%20mission%20of%20forming%20a%20government%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Mateusz%20Morawiecki%2C%E2%80%9D%20Duda%2C%20who%20was%20a%20PiS%20ally%20before%20becoming%20president%2C%C2%A0said%20in%20a%20televised%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuda%E2%80%99s%20decision%20was%20welcomed%20by%20the%20Law%20and%20Justice%20(PiS)%20party%E2%80%99s%20spokesman%2C%20Rafal%20Bochenek%2C%20who%20called%20the%20choice%20%E2%80%9Ca%20confirmation%20of%20the%20longstanding%20constitutional%20tradition%20of%20our%20country%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPiS%20the%20largest%20party%2C%20but%20without%20a%20majority%20in%20parliament%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuda%E2%80%99s%20decision%20could%20prove%20controversial%2C%20given%20that%20PiS%20lost%20its%20parliamentary%20majority%20in%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20did%20emerge%20as%20the%20largest%20single%20party%20by%20some%20margin%2C%20it%20appears%20unlikely%20that%20Morawiecki%20will%20be%20able%20to%20win%20a%20parliamentary%20vote%20of%20confidence%20and%20become%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20broad%20alliance%20of%20several%20opposition%20parties%20and%20groups%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%