ither%20lacked%20antivenoms%20or%20necessary%20equipment%20such%20as%20ventilator%20support.%20They%20lack%20training%20to%20handle%20such%20emergency%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20started%20equipping%20his%20hospital%20with%20life%20saving%20equipment%20like%20cardiac%20monitors%2C%20ventilators%2C%20and%20oxygen%20cylinders%2C%20so%20that%20he%20could%20save%20lives%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20Over%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20his%20efforts%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20mission%20that%20aims%20at%20achieving%20zero%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F78205%2Findiansnakes-jose-louies-snakebites-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnakebite%20deaths%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Dos%20%26amp%3B%20Don%E2%80%99ts%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%20Monsoons%20are%20hectic%20when%20at%20least%2012%20patients%20are%20rushed%20to%20the%20medical%20facility%20in%20a%20day.%20Without%20any%20trained%20medical%20staff%20support%2C%20the%20couple%20works%20round%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20programs%20in%20villages%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20forest%20departments%2C%20and%20medical%20colleges.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F